author: cbs8
title: Ferrari to Announce Third Quarter 2015 Results on October 28
text:
Ferrari NV
MARANELLO, Italy , Oct. 23, Ferrari N.V. (NYSE: RACE) announced today that its financial results for the third quarter of 2015 will be released on Wednesday, October 28, 2015 . A live audio webcast of the 2015 Q3 results conference call will begin at 5.30 p.m. GMT / 6.30 p.m. CET / 1.30 p.m. EDT on Wednesday, October 28 . Details for accessing this presentation are available in the Investors section of the company's website at www.ferrari.com . For those unable to participate in the live session, a replay will remain archived on the corporate website for two weeks after the call.
